322
00:36:54,190 --> 00:36:56,700
- What?!
- I got to tell you, congratulations!

323
00:36:56,910 --> 00:37:00,700
It's okay if I get a picture
of you and your men?

324
00:37:00,910 --> 00:37:03,790
Yeah. But not for publication.
Just for us!

325
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:06,620
Anything you say, Mr Ness.

326
00:37:06,830 --> 00:37:10,880
