341
00:38:20,910 --> 00:38:23,280
Part of a team.

342
00:38:24,030 --> 00:38:26,750
Teamwork...

343
00:38:29,370 --> 00:38:35,170
Looks, throws, catches, hustles.
Part of one big team.

344
00:38:36,340 --> 00:38:41,590
Bats himself the live-long day,
Babe Ruth, Ty Cobb, and so on.

345
00:38:43,350 --> 00:38:47,390
