346
00:38:49,640 --> 00:38:51,480
You follow me?

347
00:38:51,690 --> 00:38:54,400
No one.

348
00:38:54,560 --> 00:38:59,690
Sunny day, the stands are full
of fans. What does he have to say?

349
00:39:01,700 --> 00:39:05,330
I'm goin' out there for myself.

350
00:39:05,530 --> 00:39:12,040
But...I get nowhere
unless the team wins.

351
00:39:12,250 --> 00:39:14,540
- Team!
- Team.

