458
00:48:47,530 --> 00:48:51,870
Losing is half the battle.
Let's think about what is all the battle.

459
00:48:52,080 --> 00:48:54,580
Let's take the fight
to them, gentlemen!

460
00:48:54,790 --> 00:48:57,000
Thank you, Captain.

461
00:48:58,790 --> 00:49:01,880
All right! Move out!

462
