Take it easy.

463
00:49:22,780 --> 00:49:26,610
Take it easy!
lt'll all happen in time.

464
00:49:27,950 --> 00:49:30,330
This is the job.

465
00:49:30,530 --> 00:49:34,200
Don't wait for it to happen,
don't even want it to happen.

466
00:49:34,410 --> 00:49:37,040
Just watch what does happen.

467
00:49:38,250 --> 00:49:40,290
Are you my 'tutor'?

468
00:49:41,500 --> 00:49:44,340
Yes, sir, that I am.

469
00:49:47,180 --> 00:49:50,010
- Did you check it already?
- Yes, I did.

470
00:49:50,220 --> 00:49:52,310
Then leave it alone.

471
00:49:52,970 --> 00:49:55,560
You're a good cop, Giuseppe.

472
00:49:55,770 --> 00:49:59,400
